蒂娜什 (Tinashe) 继热门歌曲《Nasty》之后推出新单曲《Getting No Sleep》，并确认专辑《Quantum Baby》的发行日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/tinashe-follows-viral-hit-nasty-with-new-single-getting-no-sleep-confirms-release-date-for-album-quantum-baby- 3770630?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tinashe-follows-viral-hit-nasty-with-new-single-getting-no-sleep-confirms-release-date-for-album-quantum-babyAlex Rigotti Sun, 30 Jun 2024 15:52:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3770630 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蒂娜什（圣地亚哥·费利佩/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《量子宝贝》将是继去年《BB/Ang3l》之后三部曲的第二部</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tinashe-follows-viral-hit-nasty-with-new-single-getting-no-sleep-confirms-release-date-for-album-quantum-baby-3770630">Tinashe 继热门单曲《Nasty》之后发布了新单曲《Getting No Sleep》，确认了专辑《Quantum Baby》的发行日期，该专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蒂娜什（圣地亚哥·费利佩/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tinashe-singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tinashe">蒂娜什</a>发行了她的全新单曲“Getting No Sleep”，并确认了她的专辑“Quantum Baby”的更多细节。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tinashe-333-review-3013107">Tinashe – “333”评论：善变的明星追随她的缪斯，带来令人振奋的结果</a></li></ul><p>继《Nasty》大受欢迎之后，这位 R&amp;B 歌手于周五（6 月 28 日）发布了她的新歌，这首歌延续了她之前歌曲的俏皮感性： <em>“没有胸罩，桑塔尔，闻起来像蛋糕/所有好牙和所有金 Ace /他说，“感觉就像星期五，不同的夜晚，相同的氛围”/每次带你出去，电影场景”。</em></p><p>这位歌手还分享了她即将于 8 月 16 日发行的专辑《Quantum Baby》的发行日期。该专辑被描述为三部曲的第二部分，第一部分《BB/Ang3l》已于去年发行。</p><p> “《量子宝贝》是为了更深入地了解我，”这位音乐家在谈到这张专辑时说道。 “这是关于探索我作为一个人以及作为一名艺术家的身份。我从来都不是一个被放进盒子里的人，所以‘量子宝宝’这个名字包含了构成我作为一名创意人员的所有不同部分。”</p><p>观看下面的“失眠”视频——一开始就有针对光敏性癫痫患者的触发警告： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="蒂娜什 - 失眠" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gKj94nNuQkk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>蒂娜什最近出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaytranada-announces-new-album-timeless-with-star-studded-roster-of-collaborations-3758424">Kaytranada 的新专辑《Timeless》中，</a>她在其中出演了众多曲目，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/childish-gambino">Childish Gambino</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anderson-paak">Anderson .Paak</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thundercat">Thundercat</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/channel-tres">Channel Tres</a>等。</p><p>去年，她原定与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a>一起进行联合头条巡演，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-cancels-co-headline-tour-with-tinashe-due-to-illness-3518988">由于 Shygirl 持续患有呼吸道疾病而被迫取消</a>。</p><p>这位伦敦流行音乐实验家在一份声明中写道：“我很伤心地告诉大家，由于持续的呼吸系统疾病，我被迫做出了艰难的决定，取消即将到来的美国巡演，根据我的医生的建议，我不能手术延误时间较长。</p><p> “我也想到了 Tinashe 和 Uniiqu3，因为我们都非常期待一起参加这次巡演，”她继续说道。 “我对这种情况真的感到心碎，我希望尽快回来见到你们所有人。爱你，害羞的女孩。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，蒂娜什<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tinashe-recalls-being-forced-to-work-with-r-kelly-chris-brown-response-3498033">公开了她被迫与 R. Kelly 和 Chris Brown 合作的“尴尬”时光</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tinashe-follows-viral-hit-nasty-with-new-single-getting-no-sleep-confirms-release-date-for-album-quantum-baby-3770630">Tinashe 继热门单曲《Nasty》之后发布了新单曲《Getting No Sleep》，确认了专辑《Quantum Baby》的发行日期，该专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
社交媒体对仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 举办的 2024 年演出的反应https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-shania-twain-set-at-glastonbury-2024-3770637?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=social-media-reacts-to-仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 于格拉斯顿伯里 (2024) 拍摄Anagricel DuranSun, 30 Jun 2024 15:47:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3770637 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表演。图片来源：Joe Maher/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 演出期间的声音到底是怎么回事？”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-shania-twain-set-at-glastonbury-2024-3770637">社交媒体对 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 演出的</a>回应首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表演。图片来源：Joe Maher/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Shania-Twain-performing-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-Photo-by-Joe-Maher_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Shania-Twain">仙妮亚·唐恩</a>在今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上</a>占据了金字塔舞台，社交媒体对她的表演做出了反应。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年现场博客：周日发生的所有活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位乡村偶像在沃西农场的年度音乐盛会上表演了令人垂涎的传奇人物。吐温此前表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shania-twain-wants-to-borrow-a-horse-for-glastonbury-2024-legends-slot-3768749">她想“借”一匹马来表演，她</a>带着一群举着玩具马的变装皇后来了。</p><p>她的演出吸引了大批观众。数十万人涌向金字塔舞台观看她的表演。她以 1997 年的热门单曲《That Don&#39;t Impress Me Much》开场。</p><p>在唱完这首歌的第一句歌词后，歌迷和观众在 X/Twitter 上表达了他们对唐恩演唱的担忧。一位用户写道：“看着仙妮亚·唐恩在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表现平庸的《That Don&#39;t Impress Me Much》，我就想用一种机智的方式在推特上表达我对此的感受。”</p><p>然而，其他粉丝似乎很喜欢仙妮亚的表演，一位用户写道：“仙妮亚的表演很棒，非常愉快。”</p><p>查看以下更多反应：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">低头看着<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Glastonbury?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Glastonbury</a>宾果卡……<br /> …是的。仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 登上舞台，两侧是 S&amp;M 木马……<br />房子！！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f633.png" alt="😳" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f923.png" alt="🤣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> — 尼古拉斯·麦ツ (@NicholasMai) <a href="https://twitter.com/NicholasMai/status/1807426827482198433?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">对于仙妮亚来说，这是一个极其可怕的混音。</p><p>哎哟。</p><p> - 李·汤普森 (@leethommo) <a href="https://twitter.com/leethommo/status/1807427392324960732?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">抱歉，为什么仙妮亚·唐恩在 Glasto 听起来很糟糕？？？</p><p> — 拉拉·霍普伍德 (@larahopwood) <a href="https://twitter.com/larahopwood/status/1807427372498469314?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">看着仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 的平庸表演《That Don&#39;t Impress Me Much》，我试图想出一种机智的方式来在推特上表达我对此的感受。</p><p> - 史蒂文·基利·奥姆 (@cyclingalong) <a href="https://twitter.com/cyclingalong/status/1807426895761293476?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></scri